### 获取内存中所有已注册的 refreshableBean 类型的 beanName
GET http://localhost:8080/dynamicBean/beanNames



### 获取数据库中的所有 refreshableBean 列表
GET http://localhost:8080/dynamicBean



### 新增 bean
POST http://localhost:8080/dynamicBean
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "beanName": "test1",
  "script": "return { param -> println 'test1 running ...' } as SAM",
  "description": "test任务"
}



### 运行 bean
GET http://localhost:8080/dynamicBean/execute/test1



### 修改 bean
PUT http://localhost:8080/dynamicBean
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "beanName": "test1",
  "script": "return { param -> println 'test running 111111111...' } as SAM",
  "description": "test任务11111"
}



### 删除 bean
DELETE http://localhost:8080/dynamicBean/test1



### 新增 bean (黑名单测试)
POST http://localhost:8080/dynamicBean
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "beanName": "test2",
  "script": "return { param -> println new io.github.thetaoofcoding.sample.black.User('test') } as SAM",
  "description": "test任务"
}